have just hid this whole time.

12:04.641 --> 12:06.016
Boy, Rick,
that was some good thinking.

12:06.101 --> 12:07.518
Thanks, Morty.

12:07.602 --> 12:09.269
Yeah, it's nice to be on the
same page every once in a while.

12:09.354 --> 12:11.188
[ grunts ] You can run...

12:11.272 --> 12:14.149
but you can't hide!

12:14.234 --> 12:17.653
[ yawns ]

12:17.737 --> 12:18.946
RICK:
Oh, this is perfect, Morty. Look at that.

12:19.030 --> 12:20.197
He's getting sleepy.

12:20.281 --> 12:22.241
Just a little bit longer
before he calls it a day.

12:22.283 --> 12:23.867
That's when we make our move.

12:25.370 --> 12:27.871
[ machines whirring ]

12:30.458 --> 12:32.835
Snuffles, we didn't
mean you any harm!

12:32.919 --> 12:34.920
