12:35.004 --> 12:36.797
Dad, he wants to
be called Snowball.

12:36.881 --> 12:38.215
Well, I'm not calling him that.

12:38.299 --> 12:39.341
That's ridiculous.

12:39.426 --> 12:41.635
You're being very
aggressive, Jerry.

12:41.719 --> 12:44.471
Perhaps tomorrow Dr. Scraps
will solve that problem

12:44.556 --> 12:45.889
with a bit of surgery.

12:45.974 --> 12:47.141
[ scoffs ]

12:47.225 --> 12:49.893
